{"tid":1075557,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國軍媒：中國轟6K繞台被台灣F16戰機壓制 插入編隊之間","createTime":"2019-03-24T08:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T09:01:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b713cf60b4e65fadb325ce4c423c061e2686104a","tid":1075557,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2737278_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2737278_1.jpg&h=2bc8f9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國軍媒稱轟6K曾遭我F16以桶滾動作壓制。（圖：取自中國新浪軍事網頁）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2737278_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2737278_2.jpg&h=a547fe06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣空軍F16戰機。（記者羅添斌攝）<br />\n<br />\n〔記者羅添斌／台北報導〕中國軍機持續進行遠海長航以及繞台演訓，尤以去年4月間，10天之內就繞台演訓4次最為密集，但有中國軍媒新浪軍事最近發表專文爆料說，中國轟6K軍機在去年4月繞台演訓時，曾遭台灣F16飛行員，不僅插入轟6K戰機編隊，F16長機飛行員還以桶滾式戰術動作，繞著轟6k戰機飛行，以展示其拒統的決心。<br />\n<br />\n新浪軍事更直接點名，當時前來攔截伴飛的2架F16戰機，就是台灣空軍第4聯隊所派出。<br />\n<br />\n新浪軍事是在本月22 日發表軍事專文，並以（起底台灣空軍王牌部隊，曾駕F16繞轟6K進行桶滾動作）為題，深入探索原本稱為空軍第455聯隊，以F16戰機及S70C搜救直升機為主體的第4聯隊。<br />\n<br />\n專文中指出，在解放軍逐步換裝新式戰機之後，第4聯隊的技術優勢越來越小，但仍在與解放軍的幾次空中遭遇中，展示了其拒統的決心。<br />\n<br />\n專文說，以2018年4 月，解放軍空軍在一次繞台演訓任務期間，台灣第4聯隊出一批2架F16攔截伴飛，F16長機（戰機任務編組時，有長機與僚機之分）插入轟6K編隊之間，並在貼近轟6K長機右側之後，進行了桶滾動作。<br />\n<br />\n專文並形容，待遇良好，薪金優渥，普遍有過赴美受訓經歷的台灣空軍戰鬥機飛行員，是台軍中拒統傾向最為強烈的一個戰鬥員群體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2737278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2737278&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8qNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=5ff57259\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2737278&h=b861ecd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2737278</a>"},{"pid":"19df0d009bd7eacf5281226d5b04b1d85cfa5f59","tid":1075557,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e90ddc5b15063cee836fcc85d6ab955f1dcb7e2","tid":1075557,"uid":4496,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"支那媒體以為對面軍方主力因為待遇良好薪金優渥而效忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33ff9aa009546b2a17cfac782a5ead4c9c06915","tid":1075557,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"台灣空軍認祖歸宗，主動加入中國空軍編隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7e862d66761ad696cea429cc2d45f7c7ee33fe","tid":1075557,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e33ff9aa009546b2a17cfac782a5ead4c9c06915","tid":1075557,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"台灣空軍認祖歸宗，主動加入中國空軍編隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"屌你笑左, 笑埋右.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}